I wish my successor a year more peace of mind than we've ever had in Farmet.
The euphoria for victory soon dissipated by the impact of the crisis.
Thanks to the hard work of the winner, Farmet may already have been through the worst.
Farmet owner Karel Árský received the first prize in the latest edition of Vodafone's "Company of the Year" contest, last year at the "Slav House" in Prague.
