The second is the recovery of the framework, although it now seems like science fiction, with a very favorable current of opinion, close to 50% of the population.
The third, a redesign of the euro, in line with the German proposals for greater macroeconomic control, budgetary rigour, fines to the offending countries, possible suspensions of payments from some of them and extension to the private sector of the costs of potential adjustments.
